        {
            "title": "長和據悉考慮讓旗下屈臣氏集團上市",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"長和據悉考慮讓旗下屈臣氏集團上市\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"645\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jwGkLdamMaF3h6ALkoF55w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/51459750-c6b9-11f0-b7ba-be3adb188400\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">長和據悉考慮讓旗下屈臣氏集團上市</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
